# Frontend Design System Rules

## Typography

### Font Family
- **Primary Font**: Inter (UI text, buttons, forms)
- **Monospace Font**: Fira Code (code blocks, technical content)

### Font Weights
- Regular: 400
- Medium: 500
- Bold: 700

### Font Sizes
- xs: 12px
- sm: 14px
- base: 16px
- lg: 18px
- xl: 20px
- 2xl: 24px
- 3xl: 30px
- 4xl: 36px
- 5xl: 48px
- h1: 56px (with letter-spacing: -0.025em)
- h2: 36px (with letter-spacing: -0.025em)
- h3: 24px
- h4: 20px

### Line Heights
- tight: 1.2 (headings)
- normal: 1.6 (body text)

## Color Palette

### Background Colors
- Primary Background: #121212
- Secondary Background: #1a1a1a
- Tertiary Background: #0E0E0E
- Editor Background: #1e1e1e
- UI Element Background: #252525

### Accent Colors
- Primary Accent: #6366F1
- Success Accent: #22C55E
- Error Accent: #EF4444
- Warning Accent: #F59E0B

### Text Colors
- Primary Text: #FFFFFF
- Secondary Text: #AAAAAA

### Border Colors
- Border: #2e2e2e
- Border Hover: #3e3e3e

### Syntax Highlighting
- Keyword: #569CD6
- String: #CE9178
- Function: #DCDCAA
- Variable: #9CDCFE

## Spacing & Layout

### Element Heights
- Button Height: 40px
- Input Height: 40px
- Hero Button Height: 48px
- Navigation Height: 72px
- Sidebar Width: 240px

### Border Radius
- Small: 6px
- Medium: 8px

## Animation & Transitions

### Timing
- Fast Transition: 250ms
- Medium Transition: 350ms

### Animation Guidelines
- Use fast transitions (250ms) for interactive elements (buttons, form controls)
- Use medium transitions (350ms) for larger UI changes (panels, modals)
- Keep animations subtle and purposeful
- Ensure all animations have appropriate focus/reduced motion alternatives

## UI Component Library

### Primary UI Framework
- Tailwind CSS v4
- React 19
- Next.js 15.3.0

### Base Component Guidelines
- All interactive elements must have proper focus states
- Maintain consistent height for buttons and form controls (40px default)
- Use border-radius consistently (medium 8px for cards, small 6px for buttons)
- Implement dark theme by default with the provided color palette

### Responsive Design
- Mobile-first approach
- Breakpoints:
  - sm: 640px
  - md: 768px
  - lg: 1024px
  - xl: 1280px
  - 2xl: 1536px

### Accessibility Guidelines
- Minimum contrast ratio of 4.5:1 for text
- All interactive elements must be keyboard accessible
- Support for reduced motion preferences
- Proper ARIA attributes on custom components